        <div class="barrier-card">
            <div class="barrier-title">📋 "No time for permits"</div>
            <p style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.5;">
                Client wants to skip official approvals to save time.
            </p>
            <div class="solution-box">
                <strong>Your Response:</strong><br>
                "I understand the urgency. Let's start with interventions that don't need permits - 
                interior air sealing, roof coating. Meanwhile, I'll handle the permit paperwork 
                for the wall insulation. This way we don't delay the project."
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
        <span class="warning-icon">💡</span>
