    <h1>Natural Ventilation: Stack Effect & Night Purge</h1>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: 40px; align-items: center;">
        <div style="flex: 1;">
            <h2>How Stack Effect Works</h2>

            <div class="stack-diagram">
