            <div style="background: #f8d7da; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #721c24; font-size: 28px;">Bitumen ("Zift")</h3>
                    <ul style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.6;">
                        <li>Absorbs heat (black color)</li>
                        <li>Cracks in 6-12 months</li>
                        <li>Toxic fumes when hot</li>
                        <li>Makes problem WORSE</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #721c24; font-size: 28px;">Low-Grade Silicone</h3>
                    <ul style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.6;">
                        <li>Fails in UV exposure</li>
                        <li>Yellows and cracks</li>
                        <li>Poor adhesion when hot</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 style="color: #721c24; font-size: 28px;">Newspaper/Cardboard</h3>
                    <ul style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.6;">
                        <li>Fire hazard</li>
                        <li>Attracts pests</li>
                        <li>Zero moisture resistance</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <span class="warning-icon">⚠️</span>
